des:
Thoughts and opinions about life and other stuff from Jonathan Duhon. Let's Talk About It
Talk Bout It with Jonathan Duhon is about providing an entertaining perspective on life that will expand a persons thinking. 
Get your life and relationship questions answered with thoughts from Jonathan Duhon by Alexa. 
The database grows daily. The goal is to provide ideas to some of the most asked questions regarding the journey of living life. 
This skill will answer questions about love, life, parenting and much more.
We want this skill to encourage, uplift and expand the way people think about self-help. 
You can ask things like:
What is love?
What is loyalty?
Should I stay in a relationship?
What mindset do I need to save money?

We hope you give us a star rating because of our original content. If you think it deserves less than a 5-star rating. Let us know about it the skill and ask questions at askduhon@gmail.com and we will direct our attention immediately.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
